  "Integrating term by term: integral of 3x^2 dx = x^3, integral of -4x dx = -2x^2, integral of 7 dx = 7x. Together: x^3 - 2x^2 + 7x + C.": "",
  "What is the integral of 1/x^3 dx?": "",
